name: Asymmetry USDaf Stablecoin
reason: USDaf is a CDP stablecoin built on Liquity v2 infrastructure by Asymmetry Finance, allowing users to borrow against their BTC and Yield-Bearing Stablecoins with user-set fixed interest rates for the first time. USDaf launches May 28th and we want users to be able to find it easily on CowSwap right away!
